snippet.title: Diesel Brothers: The Game - Scrapyard Gameplay
snippet.description:
When replacements are too costly, scavenge junkyards for rusty parts. 
Add to wishlist:
➡ https://store.steampowered.com/app/750050/Diesel_Brothers_The_Game/

Running a truck tuning shop can be challenging. Sometimes you'll need to get your hands dirty to make a living. 
When replacements are too costly, scavenge junkyards for rusty parts. 
Clean 'em. Paint 'em. Use 'em! 

Stay updated:
➡ https://dieselbrothers-thegame.com
➡ https://www.facebook.com/dieselbrothersthegame/
